                    καὶ <lb/>ὁ λαὸς <expan><abbr>ἀγάλλετ</abbr><ex>αι</ex></expan>
               <lb/>διαμεῖναι τῇ <lb/>ἀγέλῃ αὐτοῦ.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation"
              ana="#b1"
              xml:id="birs0006.translation"
              corresp="#birs0006.diplomatic #birs0006.transcription">
            <p>By God has become our chief-shepherd Makaid[onios] the pious bishop, so that in
                    [his] time churches are e[rected] and are graced and the saints are adorned and
                    the people rejoice dwelling in its flock.</p>
         </div>
